WEBVTT

00:00:00.400 --> 00:00:05.779
Well, good evening, ladies and gentlemen. And to some of you, good morning, family.

00:00:05.780 --> 00:00:15.870
Praise the Lord. Thank you for joining me again tonight. I really appreciate y'all showing up every time and praying. It means a lot to me. We have work to do.

00:00:15.871 --> 00:00:37.839
But as we see some of the news today, there was an earthquake in California today, my son was telling me, and I don't know if it was too big of one, but it's an earthquake and it was on the larger scale as you all can see maybe by this map.

00:00:37.840 --> 00:01:01.107
And so I thought that was kind of interesting that it happened today as we see another vote going for a two-state solution on a very significant day, the eve of Rosh Hashanah.

00:01:01.108 --> 00:01:18.319
England made a very strong stance for a two-state solution today, from what I understand, and the only nations that sided with Israel were, I think my wife told me, three.

00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:29.452
It was a pretty clear stance, and the ones that were undecided, the number went down to like less than five or something.

00:01:29.453 --> 00:01:37.638
The numbers were ridiculous. I couldn't believe it. Actually, Australia went with it. Basically, everybody.

00:01:37.639 --> 00:01:45.978
The United States is the lone ranger out here with, I think, three other nations, but they took the vote again today.

00:01:45.979 --> 00:01:57.582
From what I understood, I was actually shocked by the level of support that voted for a two-state solution.

00:01:57.583 --> 00:02:28.399
I told my wife, I said, 'Wow, you know, okay.'But just like the Lord told us that as we enter into tomorrow, we would see the sheep and the goat nations and that a line would be drawn in the sand, and we would see the ones that will bless and the ones that will curse.

00:02:28.400 --> 00:02:35.199
And we're seeing that unfold in front of our faces at an alarming rate.

00:02:35.200 --> 00:02:41.877
So, do you have that article? Do you have that thing from your mama? I don't think so.

00:02:41.878 --> 00:02:46.228
I've written Australia, Canada, and Portugal recognize a Palestinian state.

00:02:46.229 --> 00:02:52.082
Yeah, son, but Mom had that chart, and it had each actual vote and who voted with what.

00:02:52.083 --> 00:03:01.434
But if you can't find it, that's fine. She's in there. You just have to get it from her phone. But she was telling me all that.

00:03:01.435 --> 00:03:09.638
But I'll go over some of the things that we were shown, what I was shown in prayer last night.

00:03:09.639 --> 00:03:23.136
I thought the visions last night, when the Lord was showing us about the AI and the new industrial revolution that was being displayed before me, were interesting.

00:03:23.137 --> 00:03:33.401
Every single time he shows me something, it's at a different angle. It adds to the puzzle, but it's at a different angle.

00:03:33.402 --> 00:03:44.955
And I think that is, you know, to me, I just go, 'Lord, you're so awesome.'The natural man perceiveth not the things of God. You have to get it out of the spirit.

00:03:44.956 --> 00:03:51.912
But whenever you're getting it and he's downloading things to you like he did to me last night, ladies and gentlemen, it was beautiful.

00:03:51.913 --> 00:04:02.318
The colors and the visions when the Lord is speaking to me are so full of life.

00:04:02.319 --> 00:04:10.238
You just see the colors and everything, and I try to grasp them as I'm on a live stream.

00:04:10.239 --> 00:04:31.991
When I'm in my private time and we pray, I have time to focus on each one, and I pause and I just reflect, and I'm able to really just soak in and memorize that moment in my spirit and be able to tell my wife and my children what the Lord is showing us.

00:04:31.992 --> 00:04:41.928
And when it's a live stream, because it's so public, I don't have that opportunity a lot of times because he doesn't let me park there.

00:04:41.929 --> 00:04:47.212
That's why he tells me, 'Keep going. Keep going.'Because I'm just telling you what I'm hearing.

00:04:47.212 --> 00:05:00.805
But I like to stop and soak in the moment, everything that I'm seeing, because the visions are beautiful to me. They're precious.

00:05:00.806 --> 00:05:12.719
I never just bypass them, but for the sake of time and what he's trying to do on these streams with you all is to warn you of what's coming.

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:25.839
And as we go into the 23rd in the next couple of hours here and we pray into the 23rd because I believe, you know, I believe Israel is already into the 23rd for sure by a long shot.

00:05:25.840 --> 00:05:39.593
But, you know, I'm not attacking anybody's faith of where they're believing for the 23rd and the 24th that the rapture of the church would take place.

00:05:39.594 --> 00:05:50.271
I pray you're all right. You know, that'd be awesome. But I believe that there'll be many of you that are disappointed in the next 48 hours.

00:05:50.272 --> 00:06:05.004
And I don't want you to be down. I don't want you to lose faith or lose heart in being weary in well-doing as you are still here.

00:06:05.005 --> 00:06:08.478
And you'll probably be mad at me, saying, 'Brad, I don't want to hear this,'and wanting to click off.

00:06:08.479 --> 00:06:15.519
I'm just being real with you. I just want to prepare you that we still have some work to do.

00:06:15.520 --> 00:06:27.999
I knew it, and I've tried to warn you as we're still here. And wouldn't it be wonderful if he took us right now? But I know what he's showed me.

00:06:28.000 --> 00:06:38.317
I know what I'm called to tell you to pray and that there's going to be a great shaking to awaken the church, and that the church isn't ready.

00:06:38.318 --> 00:06:49.474
The people aren't ready. They're asleep; the vast majority of the church is asleep.

00:06:49.475 --> 00:07:04.758
Yeah, we have a group of people, but you have, you know, even 100,000 people yesterday in a service with, you know, a couple million people watching on a live stream.

00:07:04.759 --> 00:07:14.478
And a lot of people called that a revival. And if that's a revival, I'm very disappointed.

00:07:14.479 --> 00:07:22.191
There are over 8 billion people on this earth. And it could be the beginning of revival.

00:07:22.192 --> 00:07:33.522
I could see maybe just the first drops of rain falling. But what is it going to take to get the people who are not even...

00:07:33.523 --> 00:07:55.010
I watched the interview from one of the CNN reporters, and he was just belligerent in what he was saying against the church and the radical evangelicals.

00:07:55.011 --> 00:08:00.314
The things that he was saying were so rude against the church, so blasphemous.

00:08:00.315 --> 00:08:08.239
But he said, 'This is my right of free speech.'And the things he was saying were poison.

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:16.399
And I watched it, and I was like, 'Wow.''This is my truth'is what he kept saying. 'This is my truth.

00:08:16.400 --> 00:08:29.560
This is my reality.'And I thought, 'Well, sir, your reality and your truth—you're a toxic, evil individual.'And I listened to it, and it was hard to swallow.

00:08:29.561 --> 00:08:35.464
It was very... I told Diana—we were watching—I said, 'This makes me boil inside.

00:08:35.465 --> 00:08:46.757
This makes me boil inside.'And I was like, 'You want to play some of it, show the worship?'There was like two hours.

00:08:46.758 --> 00:08:53.175
Let's listen to Don Lemon. Okay. Didn't know if it said Demon or Lemon.

00:08:53.176 --> 00:08:58.159
Go ahead, Don. And here is where we have to tell the truth here.

00:08:58.160 --> 00:09:02.328
Okay, so here's the truth. Don's going to break it down. Here's the media.

00:09:02.329 --> 00:09:07.883
Also, did you guys know people on the left, they don't know what just happened?

00:09:07.884 --> 00:09:16.233
If you are in your little sandbox echo chamber of the left, you don't even know if that guy was Republican, Democrat, nothing.

00:09:16.234 --> 00:09:24.398
There was a poll taken and like 10% actually knew. Like, yeah, it was just this deranged Republican.

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:31.166
What we saw in that arena was not simply faith finding public expression. Yeah, it really was.

00:09:31.167 --> 00:09:39.754
When his wife got up there and said, 'I'm going to start crying now,'and said, 'I forgive him.'Bring the tissue boxes.

00:09:39.755 --> 00:09:45.920
I will have to say that is one thing... you have him... just separates.

00:09:45.921 --> 00:09:52.730
That was a display of the truth. 'That is my truth. This is my freedom of expression.

00:09:52.731 --> 00:09:59.265
This is my First Amendment right to be able to tell you the truth from my point of view.

00:09:59.266 --> 00:10:05.062
Not just from my point of view. This is what it is.'Talk some more, Don, so we could see who you are.

00:10:05.063 --> 00:10:16.025
Oh, and the orange guy got skipped, honey. The truth is Jesus says, 'By their fruit, you'll know.'Go ahead, Don.

00:10:16.026 --> 00:10:20.530
We'll take a look at your fruit. '...was religious nationalism on full display.

00:10:20.531 --> 00:10:26.361
That is the truth. That is my truth. This is my freedom of expression.

00:10:26.362 --> 00:10:33.274
This is...'So, religious nationalism. And so as you... Am I muted?

00:10:33.274 --> 00:10:36.723
Yeah. Huh? No. No, you're not. Okay. So, religious nationalism.

00:10:36.724 --> 00:10:41.053
Some of the things that the far left, these people are saying, are very toxic.

00:10:41.054 --> 00:10:45.336
So, you listen to it and that's his truth, you know, and he's entitled to his truth.

00:10:45.337 --> 00:10:52.108
And I'm not trying to rile everybody up, but I'm trying to tell you the great deception that is upon the world.

00:10:52.109 --> 00:10:59.119
And these are the people that we're trying to reach for Jesus right now.

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:09.919
And I know there's a lot of people that are going to probably be disappointed tomorrow, is what I just know inside of what I'm hearing when I'm praying today.

00:11:09.920 --> 00:11:37.919
There's going to be a lot of people that are going to be ready to give up tomorrow because you were so focused on the rapture of the church happening tomorrow, that it's going to be one of those—do not go into a slumber, a place of depression, and just be ready to give up and let go of the rope because you're weary and well-doing.

00:11:37.920 --> 00:11:49.543
Don't become weary and well-doing. Occupy until he comes. Occupy until he comes. Be vigilant.

00:11:49.544 --> 00:12:01.620
Be aggressive about our faith of telling people that he's still coming, even if not in what you believed in your time frame as we go into tomorrow.

00:12:01.621 --> 00:12:14.078
If we come to that road—and I'm telling you, I believe we will—but if you were so strong about it, and I know there's a lot of people that got so angry at me, but I've tried to warn you.

00:12:14.079 --> 00:12:26.595
This is where I believe we are in the next 40 to 48 hours. Don't give up on everything. Keep standing. Have that backbone like a crowbar.

00:12:26.596 --> 00:12:36.129
Even if you don't see the results of what you thought you were going to see, don't give up. Have that bulldog on a bone.

00:12:36.130 --> 00:12:49.146
I'm fighting for what I believe: that Jesus Christ is coming, and he's coming back for me. He's coming back for the glorious church.

00:12:49.147 --> 00:13:04.159
But right now, I believe we're seeing the first fruits, the first little stuff here of the beginning of something major about to happen.

00:13:04.160 --> 00:13:35.363
I told the Lord when I was in my prayer time this afternoon, I was just interceding and I was praying for the church and the state of the church because I know there's a lot of you that are very upset about things, and with all the things that are going on, and some of the people that I have personally talked to over the phone praying for certain things, and visions that I have seen, wanting more to the vision.

00:13:35.364 --> 00:13:44.479
"God, show me more so I can help. Show me more."And he said, "Go back to the main thing.

00:13:44.480 --> 00:13:51.518
You never sought me for a vision. You sought me for relationship.

00:13:51.519 --> 00:14:08.239
And in relationship, the vision is shown."I've never sought him for healing gifts like that, or visions, or any kind of gifting.

00:14:08.240 --> 00:14:26.239
Everything has always been purely out of just knowing that I've had learning problems, wasn't really able to do anything. I've always been a man that has just been desperate for him.

00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:44.319
And in my desperation for him has been a byproduct of a relationship of just seeking him with all my heart, because I was not ever able to pay my bills because I wasn't able to make a lot of money because I wasn't very smart.

00:14:44.320 --> 00:14:53.557
And I said, "Father, I can't provide for this beautiful wife that I have, or these beautiful children that you've given me.

00:14:53.558 --> 00:15:08.958
And I don't like living on food stamps. I don't like living in a shotgun house in the roughest neighborhood in where I'm at.

00:15:08.959 --> 00:15:24.398
But I know that if I seek you, I'll find you, and you're going to help me with my intellect to make me something more."And in that, I lost myself in him.

00:15:24.399 --> 00:15:33.190
And I realized no matter how much I had around me, it never made me happy other than having a relationship with him.

00:15:33.191 --> 00:15:38.800
So that's where it all developed. It came out of desperation because I didn't know how to provide for my family.

00:15:38.801 --> 00:15:46.479
But then everything else became so it didn't matter anymore.

00:15:46.480 --> 00:16:02.078
I didn't care how much money I had in the bank because every day when I got home from work, I spent hours in prayer at my washing machine, doing laundry, helping my wife out.

00:16:02.079 --> 00:16:10.931
I'd sit in there and just pray and take care of my puppies, and I'd listen, and I'd be still, and I'd worship.

00:16:10.932 --> 00:16:17.599
And that's where it all developed from: a place of real desperation.

00:16:17.600 --> 00:16:28.719
And as I developed and the more I became acquainted and the more I became friends with the Father, he would come and visit.

00:16:28.720 --> 00:16:38.559
And I'm talking tangible to the point where I've had one face-to-face, flesh-to-flesh talking to him, and I thought I was going to die.

00:16:38.560 --> 00:16:53.838
Everything else has been visions. But my first physical encounter, I can tell you I thought I was going to die. My human body could not take it.

00:16:53.839 --> 00:17:04.732
It was so overwhelming, the visitation that I had, that even my wife when she came into the room, she thought I was dying because it scared her so bad.

00:17:04.733 --> 00:17:14.124
She felt the presence of the Lord. It scared her so bad in the natural that she started screaming. She said, "Oh my God, are you going?

00:17:14.125 --> 00:17:25.190
Is he taking you?"I said, "Jesus is here, and I see him."And she says, "I can't see him, but I can feel him.

00:17:25.191 --> 00:17:41.931
Please don't take my husband."She thought I was dying. I was in a pile of tears and absolute fear of God.

00:17:41.932 --> 00:18:01.918
The only thing I can tell you was it was so tangible that all I could do was just be on my face, and I was trying to just reach up and look at him because it was all I could do with the tangible presence of God in my house.

00:18:01.919 --> 00:18:19.918
Where it happened, it left a crack in the floor. And even still, as we left that house, I took pictures of that crack in the floor.

00:18:19.919 --> 00:18:48.319
And I used to tell my kids, I said, "That crack in the floor is where Jesus stood, and it left a portal in my home."I cannot tell you how, but that portal, every time I went there and I prayed in that area, I could feel the presence of God tangibly on me.

00:18:48.320 --> 00:19:01.599
And if I had hard times, I'd just go stand in that spot. But I didn't tell anybody else about it because you get weirdness, you know, like a Mary, Mother, painted figure on the wall, and people want to come and have a shrine.

00:19:01.600 --> 00:19:08.319
No, it was something private between me and my wife and my kids.

00:19:08.320 --> 00:19:22.399
But that crack in that floor, it showed up after. And I kid you not, I'll never forget that experience ever.

00:19:22.400 --> 00:19:31.279
Neither will my wife. You know, when you have an experience with Jesus, it will change you.

00:19:31.280 --> 00:19:37.839
And yeah, your flesh, you go back, you can sin, you do things because we're just human.

00:19:37.840 --> 00:19:50.639
But once you taste his glory, once you taste authentic, you'll never be the same.

00:19:50.640 --> 00:20:30.079
It does something to you. It does something to you. When you truly see his face, it does something to you.

00:20:30.080 --> 00:20:46.798
It makes you radical. I know the disciples, they got to spend those three years or so with him, and it made them radical.

00:20:46.799 --> 00:20:56.319
I can't imagine waking up every morning and having him tangibly there, Jesus Christ alive in the flesh.

00:20:56.320 --> 00:21:16.798
I had just about a five-minute encounter, if that. That one moment changed me forever. I have a lot of visions, y'all.

00:21:16.799 --> 00:21:34.158
And it's developed out of a relationship, even with what I'm telling you about raising dogs from the dead and having manifestations of even the devil.

00:21:34.159 --> 00:21:50.719
But that impartation that I got that day, my human vocabulary, even telling you right now, can't even do it justice.

00:21:50.720 --> 00:22:04.329
And it's changed my wife and I. It's changed us. But I tell you all that to say, I know more.

00:22:04.330 --> 00:22:09.805
I know when he comes and visits me, and he tells me there's more to be done.

00:22:09.806 --> 00:22:19.524
I know more about what—I know it's like I say, I go more by what he doesn't say than what he does. Do you know what I'm saying?

00:22:19.525 --> 00:22:40.319
Because we talk that much during the day and things, and he tells me, "Brandon, you have this to do, you have this planned out, and I have given you a three-year window to bring forth my people and tell them that I'm coming."Yes, sir.

00:22:40.320 --> 00:22:55.133
And the more I develop in the relationship, the relationship is no longer like a child talking to his father; it's more of an adult child.

00:22:55.134 --> 00:23:04.888
It's different instructions now. It's more like a commander-in-chief, like a boss.

00:23:04.889 --> 00:23:14.035
Some days are intimate like they used to be, but more, it's more like a commander-in-chief talking to an employee.

00:23:14.036 --> 00:23:21.839
And I don't say that disrespectfully. It's different the way he speaks.

00:23:21.840 --> 00:23:35.712
And I know it's business. He has what he wants and he will get what he wants.

00:23:35.713 --> 00:23:47.038
He is God. There's no cutting-up, funny business. Do you understand? It's serious.

00:23:47.039 --> 00:24:09.839
Before, as I was growing up and developing in this, we would talk about sports, things like that, and we still do, but there's a maturity to things.

00:24:09.840 --> 00:24:18.479
There's a maturity to things when the angels come. Now it's assignments.

00:24:18.480 --> 00:24:27.999
You know, whenever you were a child, you spoke as a child, and then you put away the childish things like the word says.

00:24:28.000 --> 00:24:36.609
That's what it's like. I let you in on a little bit of things, you know, glimpses into my life.

00:24:36.610 --> 00:24:46.505
And I'm nothing. I'm telling you all, I'm just a person that was just sold out, and he still is.

00:24:46.506 --> 00:24:53.812
And that's what I try to explain to people. The more you get hungry, the more you get thirsty, and the more you experience him.

00:24:53.813 --> 00:25:03.519
And when you have those experiences, they'll change you forever.

00:25:03.520 --> 00:25:07.272
They'll change you forever. And they changed my wife and me forever.

00:25:07.273 --> 00:25:23.918
And when he looked at me and he says certain things now, when I can see him and he's talking to me and I have these visions and I'm able to—he'll communicate with me like that.

00:25:23.919 --> 00:25:33.599
His love for humanity, his love for the people is beyond human comprehension.

00:25:33.600 --> 00:26:06.959
And when someone loves you that much and you can see the earnest, the longing for a relationship with some of you that are so lost, the compassion that he has for humanity in his eyes—it's breathtaking. How could someone love someone as much as he loves us?

00:26:06.960 --> 00:26:25.439
And as I drive around in the major cities and there's so many people in there and you go, "How do you know every single one of us?"And you know even how many hairs are upon our heads, and yet you look at somebody that seems really unlovely.

00:26:25.440 --> 00:26:36.523
Maybe they look dirty. They may be homeless and they're strung out, and yet you walk by and you may look down on them as you're driving, like, "Oh, wow.

00:26:36.524 --> 00:26:40.102
They stink,"or whatever. But he looks at each individual with love.

00:26:40.103 --> 00:26:49.918
He looks at each individual person with so much compassion and love, and there's not one of them he looks down upon.

00:26:49.919 --> 00:26:57.568
Not one. Not one does he look at as greater, and not one does he look at as any lesser than.

00:26:57.569 --> 00:27:09.119
He looks at each one as an individual that he loves compassionately and longs to have a relationship with each and every single one of you.

00:27:09.120 --> 00:27:19.678
And he's willing to do whatever it takes to get it. But there's so many people that choose hell every day.

00:27:19.679 --> 00:27:31.678
That's why he gave us free will. He gave every single one of us free will, and we choose to turn our back on him.

00:27:31.679 --> 00:27:36.719
That's why the Bible says he's an ever-present help in a time of need.

00:27:36.720 --> 00:27:44.798
He's never left us and he's never forsaken us. "Lo, until the end of the earth,"he said he'd be with us always.

00:27:44.799 --> 00:28:16.239
And even in my darkest times, and there's been some very dark days, I said, "Where are you?"He said, "Right now, you're going through refining."A true relationship is not a relationship until it's been tested.

00:28:16.240 --> 00:28:25.038
A true marriage, a real good marriage, is not a real good marriage until it's been tested.

00:28:25.039 --> 00:28:32.639
There's some refining to it. The honeymoon phase is not real marriage yet.

00:28:32.640 --> 00:28:43.678
Real marriage is when there's some challenge to it and you decide to stick together, even when you have the choice and you say, "I'm out of here.

00:28:43.679 --> 00:29:01.519
Okay, bye."Or, "I made a covenant with you, and you made a covenant with me, and no matter how dark this valley is, we're going to stick together."That's what it's like with the Lord.

00:29:01.520 --> 00:29:09.678
There's a honeymoon stage when you first get born again. There's a honeymoon stage.

00:29:09.679 --> 00:29:19.439
And whenever you develop that relationship with him and it's tested, things are tested.

00:29:19.440 --> 00:29:30.158
Remember he said, "I'll never deny you, Lord. I'll never deny you, Lord,"until it was tested.

00:29:30.159 --> 00:29:48.959
And the rooster is out there going, "Cock-a-doodle-doo."And he's sitting there going, "Oh no, he told me I'd deny him."But even when he messed up and denied him, Jesus was there saying, "And go get Peter.

00:29:48.960 --> 00:29:58.299
Go get Peter. He messed up, but I'm still merciful to him, and I'm willing to welcome him.

00:29:58.300 --> 00:30:11.759
Go get him."I was meditating today a lot upon the children of Israel.

00:30:11.760 --> 00:30:23.396
All two million of them all took the blood and put it on their door, and they were safe. No calamity came nigh them.

00:30:23.397 --> 00:30:33.359
All two million of them got the silver and the gold and marched out of Egypt, praising and worshiping the Lord.

00:30:33.360 --> 00:30:42.879
They all ate the manna. They all had their shoes and their clothes renewed. There wasn't a sick one among them.

00:30:42.880 --> 00:30:57.038
They all had their cloud by day and a fire by night, but only two made it into the promised land.

00:30:57.039 --> 00:31:07.999
There was a lot of people that saw the miracles every single day, but only two were qualified to go into the promise.

00:31:08.000 --> 00:31:22.338
God delivered them out of Egypt, but they didn't let God deliver the Egypt out of them.

00:31:22.339 --> 00:31:31.608
Egypt didn't get delivered out of them. And he was challenging me today.

00:31:31.609 --> 00:31:42.079
I was meditating on that. Only two got to go in. And there's so many people today that the Egypt's not out of you.

00:31:42.080 --> 00:31:47.997
He delivered you out of a lot of stuff. He started talking to me about that today.

00:31:47.998 --> 00:31:52.964
He said, "I've delivered them out of a lot of stuff, and I can heal you, Brandon.

00:31:52.965 --> 00:32:04.073
